section.def:
member
                                                  (會員) means any
                                                member of the Federation;

paragraph.content:
invest any surplus funds in such securities, or otherwise in such manner, as it
                may think fit, and realize the same at such times as it may consider
                necessary;

promote, control, become a member of, act as agent for, manage, superintend or
                otherwise assist any association or institution which has, either wholly or in part,
                objects which are the same as or similar to those of the Federation;
